title: I'm level 5 in honor but didn't receive any honor ward. Do anyone have any ideal?
body: My account haven't never been banned. Maybe report few time but haven't get demote from honor.

replies.body: Those ranked rewards are still in the process of being given out, so no worries just yet. If you still don't see your honor ward skin in about a week or so feel free to hit us up in a [**ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) to see about getting that added manually.
